bookTitle: Alice in the Country of Hearts, Vol. 01
bookSeries: Alice in the Country of Hearts #1
Plot: A clever retelling of the "Alice in Wonderland" tale--manga-style--this title is releasing in time for the major motion picture directed by Tim Burton and starring Johnny Depp.
